full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/25/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Immigration and Naturalization Service 300 North Los Angeles Street Los Angeles, California 90012 Refer To This File Number A17 221 191 T/C 1.130 China March 20, 1968 Mr. Do Ng 617 East Adams Blvd Los Angeles, California 90011 Please come to the office shown below at the time and place indicated in connection with an official matter. 300 North Los Angeles Street OFFICE Los Angeles, California 90012 LOCATION Room No. 8024 Floor No. 8th DATE AND HOUR Friday, April 26, 1968 - 1:45 PM ASK FOR INSPECTOR SWANSON - TRAVEL CONTROL REASON FOR Interview regarding your visa petition(s) in behalf of: APPOINTMENT WAI-OI K. NG. Any documents issued to you by this Service at any time, any BRING WITH YOU evidence you wish considered in support of your petition (see attachment re: suggested forms of evidence) and two recent passport photographs of yourself. It is important that you keep this appointment and bring this letter with you. If you are unable to do so, notify this office at once, using the reverse side of this letter, and we will make another appointment for you. Very tauly yours, ASSISTANT DISTRICT DIRECTOR TRAVEL CONTROL OFS:br Form C-56 Rev.11-24-57)
